trans-unit.source: Specifies the behaviors of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"></xref> object in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> control when the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"></xref> is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Angir virkemåten til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"> </xref> objekt i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"> </xref> kontrollerer når den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"> </xref> klikkes.

trans-unit.source: The HotSpotMode enumeration represents the behaviors that you can apply to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object within an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen HotSpotMode representerer virkemåter som du kan bruke en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objekt i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties use these enumeration values to set the behavior of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object when it is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Egenskaper bruke disse nummereringsverdier til å angi virkemåte for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objekt når den klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If both properties are set, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property specified on each individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object takes precedence over the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property on the control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis begge egenskapene er angitt, den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen som er angitt i hver enkelt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objektet overstyrer den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `HotSpotMode.NotSet` for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of an individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> gets its behavior from the containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir `HotSpotMode.NotSet` for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>for en individuell <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objektet i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>henter virkemåten fra inneholdende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In this scenario, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A> property is either `NotSet` or no value is specified, the default behavior is to navigate to a URL.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A>egenskapen er enten `NotSet` eller ingen verdi er angitt, er standardvirkemåten til å navigere til en URL-adresse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control's behavior is not specified using either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> objects it contains, by default the behavior is `HotSpotMode.Navigate`.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>virkemåten kontroll er ikke angitt ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objekter den inneholder, som standard virkemåte er `HotSpotMode.Navigate`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: In addition, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> objects that an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control contains are set to `HotSpotMode.NotSet` and no value is specified for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, the default behavior is `HotSpotMode.Navigate`.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Egenskaper i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objekter som en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontrollen inneholder er satt til `HotSpotMode.NotSet` og ingen verdi er angitt for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen standard virkemåte er `HotSpotMode.Navigate`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `HotSpotMode.Navigate` for either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, the page navigates to a URL when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir `HotSpotMode.Navigate` for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen siden navigerer til en URL-adresse når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Image.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to specify the URL to navigate to.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Image.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å angi URL-adressen til å navigere til.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Image.NavigateUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `HotSpotMode.PostBack` for either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, the page generates a postback to the server when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir `HotSpotMode.PostBack` for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen siden genererer en tilbakesending til serveren når det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> property to specify a name for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>til å angi et navn for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: This name will be passed in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs> event data when the postback event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Dette navnet vil bli sendt i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>Hendelsesdata når hendelsen sende tilbake inntreffer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: When a postback <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: Når en tilbakesending <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>klikkes, den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>denne hendelsen oppstår.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: To programmatically control the actions performed when a postback <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked, provide an event handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event.
trans-unit.target: Programmatisk styre handlingene utføres når en tilbakesending <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>er valgt, angi en hendelsesbehandling for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `HotSpotMode.Inactive` for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object does not have any behavior when it is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir `HotSpotMode.Inactive` for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objektet ikke har noen virkemåte når den klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can use this value to create an inactive hot spot within a larger active hot spot.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke denne verdien til å opprette en inaktiv hot sted i et større aktive hot sted.

trans-unit.source: This option is provided to allow you to create more complex hot spot zones within an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: Dette alternativet er angitt slik at du kan opprette mer komplekse e-soner i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: To create an inactive area within an active hot spot, you must specify the inactive hot spot before the active one in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil opprette en inaktiv område i en aktiv hot sted, må du angi inaktiv hot punktet før den aktive i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: For example, the following <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> defines an active ring by specifying an inactive circular hot spot within a larger active circular hot spot: ``` <asp:ImageMap ID="SaturnImage" ImageUrl="~/saturn.PNG" runat="server" OnClick="SaturnImage_Click"> <asp:CircleHotSpot AlternateText="planet" HotSpotMode=PostBack PostBackValue="planet" Radius=40 X=100 Y=100 /> <asp:CircleHotSpot HotSpotMode=Inactive Radius=60 X=100 Y=100 /> <asp:CircleHotSpot AlternateText="rings" HotSpotMode=PostBack PostBackValue="rings" Radius=80 X=100 Y=100 /> </asp:ImageMap> ```
trans-unit.target: For eksempel følgende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>definerer en aktiv ringen ved å angi en inaktiv sirkulære hot sted i et større aktive sirkulære hot sted: ``` <asp:ImageMap ID="SaturnImage" ImageUrl="~/saturn.PNG" runat="server" OnClick="SaturnImage_Click"> <asp:CircleHotSpot AlternateText="planet" HotSpotMode=PostBack PostBackValue="planet" Radius=40 X=100 Y=100 /> <asp:CircleHotSpot HotSpotMode=Inactive Radius=60 X=100 Y=100 /> <asp:CircleHotSpot AlternateText="rings" HotSpotMode=PostBack PostBackValue="rings" Radius=80 X=100 Y=100 /> </asp:ImageMap> ``` </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"></xref> does not have any behavior.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"> </xref> ikke har noen virkemåte.
